      <content type="html" xml:base="https://ykkim97.github.io/react-mkcomponent">&lt;p&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;table-of-contents-list&quot;&gt;React은 다음과 같이 구성되어 있습니다. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul class=&quot;table-of-contents-list&quot;&gt;
    &lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;./react-basic&quot;&gt;React란?&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
